  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e646297cf7568c040ca757196cf25027.avif?t=1742206458\" width=604 height=65 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The liquid form</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The liquid form possesses the ability to jump, swim in water, and recover health points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e7c48782a8e57261d80e46abbe1b8806.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e7c48782a8e57261d80e46abbe1b8806.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e7c48782a8e57261d80e46abbe1b8806.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The solid form</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The solid form has the ability to roll, float in water, break through obstacles, and activate mechanisms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2cef55c9166b6886b53d3487323dacb8.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2cef55c9166b6886b53d3487323dacb8.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2cef55c9166b6886b53d3487323dacb8.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The steam form</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The steam form grants the ability to fly, but it is more challenging to control. Contact with obstacles and walls can result in taking damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2c852c60a0b9ed13cbb6400b139e38ee.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2c852c60a0b9ed13cbb6400b139e38ee.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2c852c60a0b9ed13cbb6400b139e38ee.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Form transformations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross obstacles through transforming three forms , such as switching from steam to solid form at high altitude and crashing into obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8dca77e06a336dceb206e35c7de38b08.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8dca77e06a336dceb206e35c7de38b08.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8dca77e06a336dceb206e35c7de38b08.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/640d970801371435891ab33982ea160e.avif?t=1742206458\" width=604 height=65 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Push box</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e685966349b647a89ad7e595b6b24e44.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e685966349b647a89ad7e595b6b24e44.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e685966349b647a89ad7e595b6b24e44.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Electrical puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/224aacb3e7cb7a254c98ff5afcaca48b.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/224aacb3e7cb7a254c98ff5afcaca48b.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/224aacb3e7cb7a254c98ff5afcaca48b.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Optical Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e27edbe6d5699005999f83298389dd0e.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e27edbe6d5699005999f83298389dd0e.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e27edbe6d5699005999f83298389dd0e.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/a579b30fce66e85db27cabbb19c59385.avif?t=1742206458\" width=604 height=65 /></span>With simple editing of vertices, you can create terrain of various shapes, and all platforms, obstacles, and mechanisms can be freely placed. Whether the map you want to design is a difficult operation or a brain burning puzzle, everything is designed by you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At present, there are over 2000 maps  made by  players in the game. The map you created will be shared with all PC and mobile players worldwide, let's create a water-based world together!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/64f18af5ac6f625d139fa711777113da.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/64f18af5ac6f625d139fa711777113da.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/64f18af5ac6f625d139fa711777113da.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
